I'm now contemplating how to handle the existing data residing in the subcollections. Since I'm proceeding with the new top-level structure, the previous tickets in the subcollections will be invisible in the new UI. I can continue with this new structure, which functionally resets the view for new tickets, ensuring forward functionality. I've updated the permissions rule to ensure that employees can read only their data.

