I'm now solidifying the queries, ensuring correct access. I've verified that Admins use `getDocs(collection(db, 'concerns'))` for all concerns. Employees use `getDocs(query(collection(db, 'concerns'), where('employeeId', '==', uid)))` for their concerns. This setup aligns perfectly with the updated security rules, allowing admins broad access and employees a restricted view. I will update `ManageUsers.tsx` accordingly.


