I'm now integrating detailed error handling and user interface enhancements in `UploadDocuments.tsx`. I have refactored error catching by adding `storagePermissionError` and setting the UI state, stopping uploads and displaying the necessary `storage.rules`. The updated UI will display the error, guiding users to correct the issue preventing the "upload of file [from] keeping loading."


